&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own and support continuous improvement of the end-to-end delivery experience, including estimated delivery promise, shipment visibility, predictive modeling for shipment delay and notifications and logistics related experience.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop, refine, and track vendor performance metrics and internal US specific KPIs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Provide guidance, direction and feedback to Global Logistics team to drive execution excellence and consistent delivery experience improvements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead to drive US delivery projects, risk mitigation, and deliverables&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oversee training junior team members to ensure consistent understanding of processes, systems, and compliance requirements, etc.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
