&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Actively identify and scope new opportunities to improve how we serve customers and business processes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
