&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Proactively investigate beyond surface-level issues to uncover root causes and implement long-term, systemic solutions that prevent recurrence and improve delivery reliability and efficiency.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
