&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Job Summary: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;We are seeking a highly capable Inventory Transformation Process Leader to drive the evolution of our planning and execution ecosystem. This role blends deep systems expertise &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(SAP IBP) and supply chain systems expertise &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;with strong business judgement and operational pragmatism.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The successful candidate will challenge existing planning processes and systems architecture, apply &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;decision-ready data sets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;, and implement &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;exception-based planning&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt; to enable faster, higher-quality decisions. This role is hands-on and outcome-driven, focused on turning data into action and planning into a true operational decision engine.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;This is an exciting time to start this journey, providing the candidate the opportunity to blueprint and drive change. The successful candidate will bring in relevant industry experience, vision for continuous improvements, influencing ability to drive process and solution standardization, and collaboration with various stakeholders to achieve common goals, while delivering consistent and thorough deliverables as required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate will be someone who challenges “how it’s always been done”, is highly analytical, is a hands-on-leader who is equally comfortable at the whiteboard and in system configuration. One who values practical outcomes over theoretical perfection, builds systems that support how people actually work and is capable of articulating plans and ideas with all levels of the organization.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Job Expectations:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Strategy &amp;amp; Business Transformation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Partner with Supply Chain Operations, Finance, Merchandising, Marketing, and IT leaders to redefine and/or optimize &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;end-to-end planning processes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;, including Demand, Supply, Inventory, and IBP/S&amp;amp;OP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Translate business strategy into a clear, executable &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;IBP and Inventory Optimization roadmap&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Challenge legacy processes, assumptions, and system designs to improve speed, focus, and decision quality&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Drive measurable business outcomes across service, inventory, cost, and agility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
