&lt;h3&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a proactive and results-driven &lt;strong&gt;Korea Marketing Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to lead the execution of integrated marketing initiatives for the Korea market. This role will be responsible for driving localized marketing campaigns across social media, influencer marketing, promotional initiatives, and digital channels to support brand awareness, customer engagement, and business growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is a self-starter who thrives in a fast-paced environment, takes ownership of projects, and is comfortable managing multiple priorities simultaneously. You will work closely with internal cross-functional teams and external agency partners to ensure seamless execution of marketing campaigns while identifying new opportunities to grow iHerb&#39;s presence in Korea.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on role for someone who enjoys turning ideas into action, solving problems proactively, and delivering high-quality marketing execution with speed and attention to detail.&lt;/p&gt;
